{"tid":340643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[難聽過粗口] 男人應該......","createTime":"2017-07-30T06:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T09:43:53.000Z","uid":78377,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67c5174193f058fe1e702c074b5304419972c7a2","tid":340643,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"由出世到依家已經聽過呢個句式無數次<br />\n愈大就就覺得愈難聽<br />\n佼佼者一定係男人應該要有D風度<br />\n其次係係男人就應該讓下人<br />\n而我都肯撚定第一個講既係女人<br />\n然後其他女人見到work喎 就傳揚開去<br />\n普遍來講 超過9成男人都係忍氣吞聲 跟住做<br />\n但其實我想講既係<br />\n呢句野 真係好歧視 好難聽 <br />\n男人就應該 女人就唔應該？"},{"pid":"e79f787b0ecff9f51e747046609ce0a9cd7d027a","tid":340643,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"嘗試留下言 發表你既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好留低正負評就算"},{"pid":"a771734e9a62e32b708af0a150dd229562865869","tid":340643,"uid":105396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"性別定型<br />\n屋企有一個家姐，細妹加埋阿媽<br />\n中學成日比阿媽鬧<br />\n只要我老母一鬧我，剩返個兩個女人都會加把口輪我大米<br />\n然後老豆就係隔離睇電視唔出聲，間中對我投視一個愛莫能助嘅眼神<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b289ca134ca05aed6e7a47a0228c9db7f08c7ff9","tid":340643,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性別定型<br />\n屋企有一個家姐，細妹加埋阿媽<br />\n中學成日比阿媽鬧<br />\n只要我老母一鬧我，剩返個兩個女人都會加把口輪我大米<br />\n然後老豆就係隔離睇電視唔出聲，間中對我投視一個愛莫能助嘅眼神<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講 如果你本身係做錯左野 我覺得比人鬧就要企定<br />\n但唔係毫無對錯底下男人應該背負更多責任／履行非必要既義務<br />\n女性一方面想平反自己既能力 話自己乜乜(e.g. 工作)層面一樣可以同男人一樣/超越男人既成就<br />\n一方便恃女賣女<br />\n好嘔心"},{"pid":"b86bacfc381ff128ed453a6615411ddba5eca1be","tid":340643,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"留低負評既無論係巴定絲 <br />\n都想你地留低你地既意見<br />\n想知你地抱住咩心態 覺得我講得無道理"},{"pid":"f3fc1dbbcda4029c5922b446d901e94b8cafe45b","tid":340643,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"最憎做男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f785fc7986d79e56f428aab2785437e5ca091fa3","tid":340643,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最憎做男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7169094f39d0fd8124ebfd59817cdc69e3c3d5","tid":340643,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce850fb34ced7ffd10e196210d4e71ff0fa7c468","tid":340643,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:12:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b991e671cccd35570d5f1f3360b05387323b2e78","tid":340643,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"係社會做男人係辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我覺得係屋企做男人都唔錯<br />\n老母對我同家姐偏心得有d明顯<br />\n老母將家務推俾家姐做多<br />\n又話將來買樓幫俾首期<br />\n雖然佢地都鍾意家姐既<br />\n但係對待差別 連我都睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8624e28b0b675f53aad1219503631e1aecd1890","tid":340643,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係社會做男人係辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我覺得係屋企做男人都唔錯<br />\n老母對我同家姐偏心得有d明顯<br />\n老母將家務推俾家姐做多<br />\n又話將來買樓幫俾首期<br />\n雖然佢地都鍾意家姐既<br />\n但係對待差別 連我都睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然個個家庭唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c992810ea63e1c54e8837267b75320c4606ef32c","tid":340643,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"咁係因為你老竇冇撚用 但又講唔出口<br />\n你老母家姐先會乘機將個怨氣投射係你身上<br />\n<br />\n鬼叫你做錯事 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然 仲有一個可能性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主唔係佢地親生 <br />\n梗係唔洗對你咁好</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e2b53a27c15672b50a47ad8088668bfb9f9b7b","tid":340643,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係因為你老竇冇撚用 但又講唔出口<br />\n你老母家姐先會乘機將個怨氣投射係你身上<br />\n<br />\n鬼叫你做錯事 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然 仲有一個可能性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主唔係佢地親生 <br />\n梗係唔洗對你咁好</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ner... 我唔係呢個例子既受害者 <br />\n請你搞清楚"}]}